Name: Login with an existing user
Description: Test the login functionality for an existing user.

Name: Create order with invalid ingredient hash
Description: This test verifies that an order creation attempt with an invalid ingredient hash returns a 500 Internal Server Error.

Name: Create order with ingredients
Description: This test verifies that an order can be created with valid ingredients.

Name: Create order without authorization
Description: This test verifies that an order can be created without user authorization.

Name: Login with a non-existing user
Description: Test the login functionality with incorrect credentials.

Name: Get orders for authorized user
Description: This test verifies that an authorized user can successfully retrieve their orders.

Name: Create order with authorization
Description: This test verifies that an authorized user can successfully create an order with valid ingredients.

Name: Create user with empty fields
Description: Test the creation of a user with missing required fields (password) and validate the error response.

Name: Get orders for unauthorized user
Description: This test verifies that an unauthorized user cannot retrieve orders and receives a 401 Unauthorized status.

Name: Create order without ingredients
Description: This test verifies that an order creation attempt without ingredients returns the correct error.

Name: Create a unique new user
Description: Test the creation of a new unique user and validate the response.

Name: Create user that already exists
Description: Test the behavior when attempting to create a user that already exists.

Name: Edit authorized user's email
Description: Test the functionality of editing an authorized user's email.

Name: Attempt to edit user data without authorization
Description: Test the response when trying to edit user data without authorization.

Name: Edit authorized user's name
Description: Test the functionality of editing an authorized user's name.
